    {
      "id": "candidate-program-wave-note",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Suggested Waves",
      "position": {
        "x": 1080,
        "y": -110
      },
      "width": 460,
      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Suggested Waves\n\nWave 1:\n- planning\n- agent / prompting\n- product / project\n- knowledge / research\n\nWave 2:\n- workflow / execution\n- document / publishing\n- data / schema\n- UI / interaction\n\nExploratory / later:\n- spatial / environment\n- narrative / story\n\nReasoning:\n- wave 1 stays closest to Twilite's current graph-as-work surface\n- wave 2 depends on stronger runtime, composition, and schema support\n- exploratory families need sharper product pull before implementation",
        "_classBinding": {
